- ♪ BA-BA, BA-BA ♪

20:43.408 --> 20:45.577
♪ BA-BA, BA-BA ♪

20:50.457 --> 20:52.793
♪ BA-BA, BA-BA ♪

20:52.876 --> 20:55.128
♪ BA-BA, BA-BA ♪

